# Web3Forms — forwards /contact submissions to your inbox.
# 1. Sign up at https://web3forms.com with support@roncyo.com
# 2. Copy your Access Key
# 3. In Web3Forms dashboard, restrict the key to https://roncyo.com
# 4. Add in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables:
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
